summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Whitman Avenue from No. 59th Street to No. 62nd Street et al in the City of Seattle, by grading under Ordinance No. 20400, creating Local Improvement District No. 1995 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
